Start the mock server

Usage:
  mockserver [--port N --host IP --root PATH]
  mockserver (-h|--help)

Options:
  -p --port N
    Port number [default: 3000]

  -b --host IP
    Binding address [default: 0.0.0.0]

  -r --root PATH
    Root mocks directory [default: ./mocks]

  -h --help
    Show this help

  --version
    Show version number
